                    A copy of the document can be download at HKSAR - Security Regulations .
                    <br><br>
                </div>
                <footer class="w3-container" style="color: #fff !important; background-color: #0C6390 !important; height: 50px;">
                    <p></p>
                </footer>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
